    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The continuation of the beloved series takes you on a new journey across Europe — more countries, more mysteries, and brand-new mini-games. You’ll explore ancient cities, cozy streets, and dozens of hidden objects scattered among stunning European landscapes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159060/extras/9ed3912e30d4a4f1e61b27f2e332c1b7.poster.avif?t=1759764326\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159060/extras/9ed3912e30d4a4f1e61b27f2e332c1b7.webm?t=1759764326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159060/extras/9ed3912e30d4a4f1e61b27f2e332c1b7.mp4?t=1759764326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit the Bullring in Seville, stroll through the vineyards of La Rioja, see the ancient San Sebastian lighthouse, enjoy the theme park in Senlis, France, and take a walk along the canals of Venice. Along the way, you’ll explore national parks, visit a luxurious casino in Monaco, step into two fascinating museums and an ancient castle, and discover more about Europe’s rich musical culture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159060/extras/9ea10c7f58703626f0204e0c2754a74c.poster.avif?t=1759764326\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159060/extras/9ea10c7f58703626f0204e0c2754a74c.webm?t=1759764326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159060/extras/9ea10c7f58703626f0204e0c2754a74c.mp4?t=1759764326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <strong>Game Features:</strong><br>• Over 15 beautiful hidden-object locations<br>• Find more than 500 hidden items and a cute raccoon on every level<br>• Over 15 unique new mini-games<br>• Beautiful desktop wallpapers<br>• A collectible album with virtual postage stamps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This new chapter keeps the warm atmosphere of previous games while adding even more details, puzzles, and visual surprises. It’s a calm and cozy journey where every level feels like a postcard from Europe — full of charm and little treasures waiting to be found.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
